  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON:  Due to size, bulk and design of the signs, and method of internal illumination the fascia light box and double sided internally illuminated projecting sign box would detract from host building which is locally listed, the streetscene and the Angel Conservation Area and the setting of the Grade II Listed Building, the Business Design Centre.   The proposal is contrary to PPS5 “Planning and the Historic Environment”, policies D4 (Designing in context), D11 (Alteration and Extensions) and ENV11 (Advertisements and Signs) of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002 and the guidance set out in the Conservation Area Design Guidelines 2002 and the Shopfront Design Guide."
